title: Bottom View Toolbar
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The main view toolbar is now a separate bar at the bottom of each tiddler, but actions can now be added to any corner of the view frame, except the upper-left one. Use the tags $:/tags/ViewToolbar/Title, $:/tags/ViewToolbar/BottomLeft and $:/tags/ViewToolbar/BottomRight instead of $:/tags/ViewToolbar.

The action button icons are replaced with Material Icons.